  "description": "<p>英国最大的酒店连锁准备开启一系列新的经济型城市酒店，这些智能化旅店将提供基于应用的入住服务，为客人提供更好的个性化服务。<strong>Whitbread将在伦敦科芬园于2014年秋季开启Premier Inn总理酒店，内部提供床铺、浴室、免费的Wi-Fi、桌子和40英寸的智能电视，更重要的是这些房间是完全智能化的。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e1a40e2/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243216.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%86%E5%BC%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97+%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%86%E7%94%B1%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243216.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%86%E5%BC%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97+%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%86%E7%94%B1%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243216.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%86%E5%BC%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97+%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%86%E7%94%B1%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243216.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%86%E5%BC%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97+%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%86%E7%94%B1%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/e